---
OpenSkyhawk Client speaks to and bundles control-reference data derived from
DCS-BIOS (https://github.com/dcs-bios/dcs-bios), which is licensed GPL v2 — that
is why this client is GPL-2.0-only (matching DCS-BIOS). It is part of the
OpenSkyhawk project (https://github.com/OpenSkyHawk). DCS-Skunkworks/Bort
(GPL-3.0) is referenced as a design precedent only; no Bort source is copied.

Note: the GPL guarantees the freedom to use the software for any purpose,
including commercial use — it does not (and cannot) impose a non-commercial
restriction.
